for photoshop:
install photoshop, there are two keygen for adobe. first generate key with "Photoshop CS3 Extended Keygen VLK" paste it on adobe Then, choose Other Activation Options, select Over The Telephone, now adobe ll give you Activation Number, copy the Activation Number and open the second keygen "MasterCollectionCS3KEYGEN" now paste the activation no on activation field and generate Authorization code, now copy the Authorization code except the last 4 digits and paste it on adobe Authorization field. The last 4 digits should come from the activation number the program gave you (usually 6495).
cheers.....
